text: Jenelli Fraser (born July 7, 1991) is a Belizean beauty pageant titleholder who was crowned Miss Universe Belize 2018. As Miss Universe Belize, she will represent Belize at Miss Universe 2018. ==Pageantry== In the months leading up to the pageant, Fraser says that it was "very difficult" to enter the pageant, due to financial issues.
